{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856967365,"sessionID":"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3","part":{"id":"prt_d7952de8c001M35BVzgdjMnhBF","messageID":"msg_d7952cb92001trocULGR3PdCTk","sessionID":"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-bea4ffdbfc7d4509bdee5e3f2e68bc1b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # delta-spec.md — AR-013: Redis 存储实现\n2: \n3: ## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n4: \n5: ## Delta Overview\n6: \n7: 新增 Redis/Valkey 后端实现，用于持久化 sandbox 元数据。支持按 session ID 存储、检索、更新和删除，并提供基于过期时间和最后活动时间的索引查询。\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## 新增接口和类型\n12: \n13: ### Requirement: Store interface contract\n14: \n15: 系统 SHALL 提供 `Store` 接口，由 Redis 和 Valkey 提供商实现。\n16: \n17: ```go\n18: type Store interface {\n19:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n20:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n21:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n22:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n23:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n24:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n25:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n26:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n27:     Close() error\n28: }\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\n32: \n33: - **GIVEN** 一个健康的 Redis/Valkey 服务器\n34: - **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\n35: - **THEN** 实现发送 PING 命令并要求返回字符串 `PONG`\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## 错误处理\n40: \n41: ### Requirement: Not found semantics\n42: \n43: 系统 SHALL 返回包级错误 `ErrNotFound`（消息 `store: not found`），当 session key 在读取时不存在，或最后活动时间更新指向缺失的 session 时。\n44: \n45: ```go\n46: var ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"store: not found\")\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### Scenario: Get missing session\n50: \n51: - **GIVEN** 后端不存在 key `session:{id}`\n52: - **WHEN** 执行 `GetSandboxBySessionID`\n53: - **THEN** 错误为 `ErrNotFound`（Redis: `Nil`；Valkey: `IsValkeyNil`）\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## 数据存储键设计\n58: \n59: ### Requirement: Session key naming\n60: \n61: 系统 SHALL 使用字符串前缀 `session:` 与 session id 拼接作为 JSON 文档存储的主键。\n62: \n63: ### Scenario: Key construction\n64: \n65: - **GIVEN** session id `abc`\n66: - **WHEN** 存储写入 sandbox 数据\n67: - **THEN** 字符串 key 为 `session:abc`\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## 索引设计\n72: \n73: ### Requirement: Expiry index\n74: \n75: 系统 SHALL 维护有序集合 key `session:expiry`，成员为 session id，分数为 `ExpiresAt` Unix 秒数。`StoreSandbox` SHALL 添加成员并使用 sandbox 过期分数。`DeleteSandboxBySessionID` SHALL 删除成员。\n76: \n77: ### Scenario: List expired uses ZRANGEBYSCORE\n78: \n79: - **GIVEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` 且 limit > 0\n80: - **WHEN** 实现查询索引\n81: - **THEN** 选择分数从负无穷到 `before.Unix()` 的成员，限制为 `limit` 条\n82: \n83: ### Requirement: Last-activity index\n84: \n85: 系统 SHALL 维护有序集合 key `session:last_activity`，成员为 session id，分数为最后活动 Unix 秒数。`StoreSandbox` SHALL ZADD 分数为 `time.Now().Unix()`。`UpdateSessionLastActivity` SHALL ZADD 提供的时间戳（或零时使用当前时间）。`DeleteSandboxBySessionID` SHALL ZREM 成员。\n86: \n87: ### Scenario: List inactive uses activity index\n88: \n89: - **GIVEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)`\n90: - **WHEN** 执行\n91: - **THEN** 返回最后活动分数 ≤ `before.Unix()` 的成员，最多 `limit` 条\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## 存储操作\n96: \n97: ### Requirement: StoreSandbox atomicity and validation\n98: \n99: 系统 SHALL 拒绝 nil sandbox 或零 `ExpiresAt`。系统 SHALL 在一个 pipeline/multi 块中执行 session key 的 SETNX、ZADD expiry 和 ZADD last_activity。系统 SHALL 如果批处理中任何命令错误则失败。\n100: \n101: ### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected\n102: \n103: - **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, nil)`\n104: - **WHEN** 调用\n105: - **THEN** 错误指示 sandbox 为 nil\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## 更新操作\n110: \n111: ### Requirement: UpdateSandbox semantics\n112: \n113: 系统 SHALL 仅使用 SET with XX（key 必须存在）更新 session JSON 值。系统 SHALL 在此操作中不修改 expiry 或 last-activity ZSET 条目。\n114: \n115: ### Scenario: Missing key on update\n116: \n117: - **GIVEN** session key 不存在\n118: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox` 运行\n119: - **THEN** Redis: SETXX 返回 false → 错误 `key not exists`；Valkey: 响应非 OK → 同类错误\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ## 删除操作\n124: \n125: ### Requirement: DeleteSandboxBySessionID cleanup\n126: \n127: 系统 SHALL 在一个 pipeline/multi 中删除 session key 并从两个有序集合中移除 session id。\n128: \n129: ### Scenario: Full removal\n130: \n131: - **GIVEN** 一个存在的 session\n132: - **WHEN** 删除成功\n133: - **THEN** GET session key 返回 not found，ZSET 不再包含该成员\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## 查询操作\n138: \n139: ### Requirement: List loaders tolerate missing keys\n140: \n141: 当按 ZSET 列出返回 session id 时，系统 SHALL 按 id 加载 JSON；如果字符串 key 缺失 SHALL 跳过条目（Redis pipeline GET nil，Valkey MGET 空字符串）而不导致整个批处理失败。\n142: \n143: ### Scenario: Orphan ZSET member\n144: \n145: - **GIVEN** ZSET 中的 session id 没有对应的 hash/string 值\n146: - **WHEN** `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` 运行\n147: - **THEN** 该 id 从返回的 slice 中省略\n148: \n149: ---\n150: \n151: ## 活动更新\n152: \n153: ### Requirement: UpdateSessionLastActivity preconditions\n154: \n155: 系统 SHALL 拒绝空 session id。如果 `at` 为零时间，系统 SHALL 使用 `time.Now()`。系统 SHALL 在 ZADD 前验证 session key 存在；如果不存在 SHALL 返回 `ErrNotFound`。\n156: \n157: ### Scenario: Activity bump for unknown session\n158: \n159: - **GIVEN** 没有 `session:{id}` key\n160: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity`\n161: - **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## 后端选择\n166: \n167: ### Requirement: Provider selection via STORE_TYPE\n168: \n169: 系统 SHALL 不区分大小写读取 `STORE_TYPE`；如果未设置 SHALL 默认为 `redis`。支持的值 SHALL 为 `redis` 和 `valkey`；任何其他值 SHALL 导致初始化失败。\n170: \n171: ```go\n172: const (\n173:     redisStoreType  string = \"redis\"\n174:     valkeyStoreType string = \"valkey\"\n175: )\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ### Scenario: Default redis\n179: \n180: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` 未设置\n181: - **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次初始化\n182: - **THEN** Redis 实现被构造\n183: \n184: ---\n185: \n186: ## Redis 配置\n187: \n188: ### Requirement: Redis environment and password policy\n189: \n190: 系统 SHALL 要求 `REDIS_ADDR`。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `REDIS_PASSWORD`，除非 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 不区分大小写设置为 false。\n191: \n192: ### Scenario: Password required by default\n193: \n194: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` 设置且 `REDIS_PASSWORD` 为空且 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 未设置\n195: - **WHEN** Redis store 初始化\n196: - **THEN** 初始化失败，错误提示需要密码\n197: \n198: ---\n199: \n200: ## Valkey 配置\n201: \n202: ### Requirement: Valkey environment and options\n203: \n204: 系统 SHALL 要求 `VALKEY_ADDR`（逗号分隔的地址拆分为 `InitAddress`）。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `VALKEY_PASSWORD`，除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`。系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` 解析为 true 时设置 `DisableCache` 为 true；系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` 解析为 true 时设置 `ForceSingleClient` 为 true。\n205: \n206: ### Scenario: Optional client flags\n207: \n208: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true`\n209: - **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\n210: - **THEN** `ClientOption` 上的 `DisableCache` 为 true\n211: \n212: ---\n213: \n214: ## 单例访问\n215: \n216: ### Requirement: Singleton access\n217: \n218: 系统 SHALL 使用 `sync.Once` 暴露 `func Storage() Store`；失败的 init SHALL 通过 klog 记录 fatal。\n219: \n220: ```go\n221: func Storage() Store\n222: func initStore() error\n223: ```\n224: \n225: ### Scenario: Single initialization\n226: \n227: - **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 调用 `Storage()`\n228: - **WHEN** 它们并发运行\n229: - **THEN** `initStore` 恰好执行一次\n230: \n231: ---\n232: \n233: ## 存储的数据结构\n234: \n235: ### SandboxInfo 结构体\n236: \n237: ```go\n238: type SandboxInfo struct {\n239:     Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n240:     SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n241:     SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n242:     Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n243:     EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n244:     SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n245:     CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n246:     ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n247:     Status           string              `json:\"status\"`\n248: }\n249: \n250: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n251:     Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n252:     Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n253:     Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n254: }\n255: ```\n256: \n257: ---\n258: \n259: ## Redis 实现细节\n260: \n261: ### Requirement: RedisStore struct\n262: \n263: Redis 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` 客户端。\n264: \n265: ```go\n266: type redisStore struct {\n267:     cli                  *redisv9.Client\n268:     sessionPrefix        string\n269:     expiryIndexKey       string\n270:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n271: }\n272: ```\n273: \n274: ### Requirement: Fixed key patterns\n275: \n276: | Field | Value |\n277: |-------|--------|\n278: | `sessionPrefix` | `\"session:\"` |\n279: | `expiryIndexKey` | `\"session:expiry\"` |\n280: | `lastActivityIndexKey` | `\"session:last_activity\"` |\n281: \n282: ### Scenario: Redis operations summary\n283: \n284: | Method | Redis commands |\n285: |--------|----------------|\n286: | `Ping` | `PING` → expect `PONG` |\n287: | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `GET session:{id}` |\n288: | `StoreSandbox` | Pipeline: `SETNX`, `ZADD session:expiry`, `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n289: | `UpdateSandbox` | `SET key value XX` |\n290: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | Pipeline: `DEL`, `ZREM expiry`, `ZREM last_activity` |\n291: | `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry -inf {before.Unix} LIMIT 0 limit` then pipeline GETs |\n292: | `ListInactiveSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity ...` then pipeline GETs |\n293: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `GET` (existence), then `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n294: | `Close` | `cli.Close()` |\n295: \n296: ---\n297: \n298: ## Valkey 实现细节\n299: \n300: ### Requirement: ValkeyStore struct\n301: \n302: Valkey 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端。\n303: \n304: ```go\n305: type valkeyStore struct {\n306:     cli                  valkey.Client\n307:     sessionPrefix        string\n308:     expiryIndexKey       string\n309:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n310: }\n311: ```\n312: \n313: ### Scenario: Valkey operations summary\n314: \n315: | Method | Valkey API |\n316: |--------|------------|\n317: | `Ping` | `B().Ping()` → string `PONG` |\n318: | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `B().Get().Key(key)` → bytes; `IsValkeyNil` → `ErrNotFound` |\n319: | `StoreSandbox` | `DoMulti`: `SETNX`, `ZADD` expiry, `ZADD` last_activity |\n320: | `UpdateSandbox` | `SET ... XX`; success requires `ToString() == \"OK\"` |\n321: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | `DoMulti`: `DEL`, `ZREM` expiry, `ZREM` last_activity |\n322: | `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\"-inf\")`, `Max(fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\", before.Unix()))`, `Limit(0, limit)` |\n323: | `ListInactiveSandboxes` | Same on `last_activity` key |\n324: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `Exists` key → int64 must be 1; then `Zadd` |\n325: | `Close` | `vs.cli.Close()` then return nil |\n326: \n327: ---\n328: \n329: ## 依赖项\n330: \n331: ### Requirement: Package imports\n332: \n333: ```go\n334: import (\n335:     \"context\"\n336:     \"time\"\n337:     \"sync\"\n338: \n339:     \"github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\"\n340:     \"github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\"\n341:     \"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n342:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n343: )\n344: ```\n\n(End of file - total 344 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# delta-spec.md — AR-013: Redis 存储实现\n\n## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n\n## Delta Overview\n\n新增 Redis/Valkey 后端实现，用于持久化 sandbox 元数据。支持按 session ID 存储、检索、更新和删除，并提供基于过期时间和最后活动时间的索引查询。\n\n---\n\n## 新增接口和类型\n\n### Requirement: Store interface contract\n\n系统 SHALL 提供 `Store` 接口，由 Redis 和 Valkey 提供商实现。\n\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n    GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775856967348,"end":1775856967362}}}}
